♪ Fast ♪

1:39:06.691 --> 1:39:13.031
♪ The color’s draining out ♪

1:39:13.114 --> 1:39:19.037
♪ And it feels as if the fun ♪

1:39:19.120 --> 1:39:22.999
♪ Sweeps away ♪

1:39:23.083 --> 1:39:25.960
♪ The shame ♪

1:39:26.044 --> 1:39:31.716
♪ Of looking
through these eyes ♪

1:39:33.009 --> 1:39:38.932
♪ A harsh, bright
morning light ♪

1:39:39.015 --> 1:39:45.397
♪ This town could be on fire ♪

1:39:46.606 --> 1:39:52.237
♪ Far from the sky ♪

1:39:52.320 --> 1:39:58.993
♪ But you and I ♪

1:39:59.077 --> 1:40:05.583
♪ Can run to something else ♪

1:40:05.667 --> 1:40:12.257
♪ With all we left behind ♪

1:40:12.340 --> 1:40:18.722
♪ It’s you and I ♪

1:40:18.805 --> 1:40:22.225
♪ That’s left ♪

1:40:22.308 --> 1:40:27.939
♪ Alone in this ♪

1:40:28.022 --> 1:40:30.191
♪ ♪

1:40:39.701 --> 1:40:42.537
♪ These ♪

1:40:42.620 --> 1:40:46.082
♪ Stars ♪

1:40:46.166 --> 1:40:49.043
♪ Don’t ♪

1:40:49.127 --> 1:40:51.963
♪ Shine ♪

1:40:52.046 --> 1:40:57.886
♪ They’re just pinholes
in the dark ♪

1:40:59.179 --> 1:41:05.602
♪ What lies behind is bright ♪

1:41:05.685 --> 1:41:08.813
♪ Sharp ♪

1:41:08.897 --> 1:41:12.066
♪ Real ♪

1:41:12.150 --> 1:41:18.782
♪ I can’t draw it for you ♪

