♪ You have to see for yourself ♪

1:41:24.662 --> 1:41:30.752
♪ This town could be on fire ♪

1:41:32.295 --> 1:41:37.967
♪ Far from the sky ♪

1:41:38.051 --> 1:41:44.849
♪ But you and I ♪

1:41:44.933 --> 1:41:51.147
♪ Will run behind the light ♪

1:41:51.231 --> 1:41:55.693
♪ With all we left behind ♪

1:41:55.777 --> 1:41:58.780
♪ All we left behind ♪

1:41:58.863 --> 1:42:04.494
♪ It’s you and I ♪

1:42:04.577 --> 1:42:07.455
♪ That’s left ♪

1:42:07.539 --> 1:42:14.462
♪ Alone in this ♪

1:42:18.550 --> 1:42:20.677
[song ends]

1:42:20.760 --> 1:42:22.929
♪ ♪

1:42:52.792 --> 1:42:54.961
♪ ♪

